She's flirting.

273
00:19:15.041 --> 00:19:18.378
But seriously.
this is tremendously exciting.

274
00:19:18.586 --> 00:19:21.673
The knowledge. the new ideas:
it'll change everything.

275
00:19:22.090 --> 00:19:24.008
And we must be open to it.

276
00:19:24.175 --> 00:19:26.761
Maybe they can tell us about our universe.

277
00:19:26.844 --> 00:19:28.179
How it started.

278
00:19:28.346 --> 00:19:29.847
Where it's going.

279
00:19:30.014 --> 00:19:32.267
Perhaps even its purpose.

280
00:19:33.017 --> 00:19:34.602
It's tremendously exciting.

281
00:19:34.686 --> 00:19:37.355
It's the most important event since...

282
00:19:37.689 --> 00:19:39.941
...Jesus walked in Galilee--

283
