304
00:20:59.272 --> 00:21:01.441
He made the international sign
of the doughnut.

305
00:21:02.025 --> 00:21:06.363
From the limited information available.
I've made three extrapolations. One:

306
00:21:06.529 --> 00:21:09.366
Our Martian friend
is a carbon-based life form.

307
00:21:09.532 --> 00:21:11.701
Two: He breathes nitrogen.

308
00:21:11.868 --> 00:21:12.953
And three:

309
00:21:13.036 --> 00:21:16.039
The large cerebrum here. indicates...

310
00:21:16.539 --> 00:21:18.458
...telepathic potential.

311
00:21:18.875 --> 00:21:20.377
You mean they can...

312
00:21:20.460 --> 00:21:22.045
...read our thoughts?

313
00:21:23.630 --> 00:21:25.131
Potentially. yes.

314
00:21:25.298 --> 00:21:27.467
What about their intentions?

315
00:21:27.634 --> 00:21:29.302
Are they friendly people?

316
00:21:29.386 --> 00:21:34.224
Logic dictates that given
their high level of technical development...

317
00:21:34.558 --> 00:21:36.476
...they're an advanced culture.

318
00:21:36.560 --> 00:21:39.396
Therefore. peaceful and enlightened.

319
00:21:40.230 --> 00:21:42.566
The human race. on the other hand...

320
00:21:42.983 --> 00:21:45.986
...is an aggressively dangerous species.

321
00:21:46.903 --> 00:21:49.990
Now I suspect they have
more to fear from us...

322
00:21:50.156 --> 00:21:51.741
...than we from them.

323
00:21:52.576 --> 00:21:53.577
Doctor.

324
00:21:53.994 --> 00:21:55.120
Thank you.

325
00:21:56.246 --> 00:22:00.083
For many years.
I've been refining a translating computer.

326
00:22:01.002 --> 00:22:03.921
The results are not perfect. but this...

327
00:22:04.088 --> 00:22:06.424
...may answer some of your questions.

328
00:22:12.221 --> 00:22:13.806
Green skin...

329
00:22:14.557 --> 00:22:16.726
...800 centuries ago.

330
00:22:17.143 --> 00:22:18.728
Their bodily fluids...

331
00:22:18.895 --> 00:22:21.397
...include the birth of half-breeds.

332
00:22:21.814 --> 00:22:23.357
How many centuries did he say?

333
00:22:23.441 --> 00:22:24.442
Eight hundred. sir.

334
00:22:24.525 --> 00:22:26.819
Self-determination of the cosmos.

335
00:22:27.820 --> 00:22:30.406
For dark is the suede that...

336
00:22:30.573 --> 00:22:31.741
...mows...

337
00:22:31.991 --> 00:22:34.076
