338
00:22:34.660 --> 00:22:36.621
What the hell does that mean?

339
00:22:51.677 --> 00:22:52.845
Hey. Mitch.

340
00:22:52.929 --> 00:22:54.222
Good morning.

341
00:22:54.347 --> 00:22:57.934
I'm sorry. you can't come this way.
There's a tour in progress.

342
00:23:06.944 --> 00:23:08.737
Hello. my name is Barbara.

343
00:23:08.820 --> 00:23:10.489
Hello. Barbara.

344
00:23:11.156 --> 00:23:15.327
I am an alcoholic.
but I haven't had a drink in three months.

345
00:23:21.959 --> 00:23:25.295
I'm feeling so optimistic
because of the Martians.

346
00:23:25.963 --> 00:23:28.382
We're not alone in the universe.

347
00:23:28.715 --> 00:23:30.717
And it's so perfect...

348
00:23:30.884 --> 00:23:34.429
