...so many people unhappy in their lives.

352
00:23:45.649 --> 00:23:46.817
And then...

353
00:23:47.484 --> 00:23:51.071
...the Martians heard
our global karmic cry for help.

354
00:23:51.655 --> 00:23:53.156
People say they're ugly...

355
00:23:53.240 --> 00:23:55.993
