to show us the way.

356
00:23:58.079 --> 00:24:00.415
I think they've come to save us.

357
00:24:03.376 --> 00:24:04.502
Thank you.

358
00:24:17.181 --> 00:24:18.266
Bye-bye.

359
00:24:18.349 --> 00:24:21.269
You be careful. Don't get yourself killed.

360
00:24:21.436 --> 00:24:22.854
Ain't she cute?

361
00:24:23.021 --> 00:24:25.440
-We're real proud of you.
-Thanks. Dad.

362
00:24:26.774 --> 00:24:28.192
Let me take this.

363
00:24:29.694 --> 00:24:33.698
So long. retard. Don't touch
any of my stuff while I'm gone.

364
00:24:35.783 --> 00:24:37.201
Bye-bye. Grandma.

365
00:24:37.368 --> 00:24:38.620
Good-bye. Thomas.

366
00:24:38.703 --> 00:24:40.121
It's Billy-Glenn. Grandma.

367
00:24:40.204 --> 00:24:41.789
I know. Thomas.

368
00:24:43.708 --> 00:24:45.043
Bye-bye. honey.

369
