387
00:26:20.974 --> 00:26:22.309
I want to see...

388
00:26:22.475 --> 00:26:23.727
...Slim...

389
00:26:23.894 --> 00:26:25.228
...and Muffy...

390
00:26:25.645 --> 00:26:26.980
...and Richie.

391
00:26:29.983 --> 00:26:31.526
Grandma. I'm Richie.

392
00:26:33.069 --> 00:26:34.988
I know. Thomas.

393
00:26:35.322 --> 00:26:37.908
