485
00:34:08.324 --> 00:34:10.034
Positively positive.

486
00:34:10.201 --> 00:34:11.786
We don't want any slip-ups.

487
00:34:11.869 --> 00:34:13.997
No. no. no. no. Not at all.

488
00:34:35.518 --> 00:34:38.313
Poppy. All these people.

489
00:34:39.147 --> 00:34:41.524
All of them here to see you.

490
00:34:44.319 --> 00:34:46.154
There's Jason. Poppy!

491
00:34:59.001 --> 00:35:00.502
Okay. let's go.

492
00:35:02.713 --> 00:35:06.091
The teeming masses have gathered
