495
00:35:09.678 --> 00:35:12.056
Curiosity? Or is it something more?

496
00:35:12.389 --> 00:35:15.100
Or simply to say. 'I was there'?

497
00:35:15.559 --> 00:35:16.936
'I was there...

498
00:35:17.102 --> 00:35:18.687
