503
00:35:57.477 --> 00:35:58.645
Some room.

504
00:35:58.812 --> 00:36:00.605
Give them room.

505
00:36:52.490 --> 00:36:54.701
It is an awesome sight.

506
00:36:54.868 --> 00:36:57.829
The giant spacecraft glinting...

507
00:36:57.997 --> 00:37:00.666
