516
00:37:51.092 --> 00:37:52.760
Gee whiz.

517
00:38:21.081 --> 00:38:22.416
Martians!

518
00:38:23.417 --> 00:38:25.127
Funny little critters.

519
00:39:04.000 --> 00:39:05.168
Well?

520
00:39:06.127 --> 00:39:07.045
Wait.

521
00:39:10.798 --> 00:39:11.925
Greetings.

522
00:39:12.133 --> 00:39:14.636
I am the Martian ambassador.

523
00:39:17.138 --> 00:39:19.807
Everything is fixed now. You may speak.

524
00:39:19.974 --> 00:39:21.309
Greetings.

525
00:39:21.476 --> 00:39:23.061
I am General Casey...

526
00:39:23.144 --> 00:39:27.815
...Commanding Officer of the Armed
Forces of the United States of America.

527
00:39:28.191 --> 00:39:30.818
On behalf of the people of Earth:

528
00:39:30.985 --> 00:39:32.028
Welcome.

529
00:39:32.862 --> 00:39:34.280
He did that well.

530
00:40:04.562 --> 00:40:06.063
We come in peace.

531
00:40:06.897 --> 00:40:09.066
We come in peace. We come in peace.

532
00:40:13.988 --> 00:40:16.156
They came in peace.

533
00:40:19.326 --> 00:40:20.995
We come in peace.

534
00:40:50.357 --> 00:40:51.442
Open fire!

535
00:41:23.058 --> 00:41:24.226
What?

536
00:42:13.859 --> 00:42:16.362
